msgctxt "56_Baby"
msgid "Goo goo..."
msgstr "Gu, gu..."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "68_Date"
msgid "We did it, Kiryu! He stopped crying!"
msgstr "¡Lo logramos, Kiryu! ¡Dejó de llorar!"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "80_Kiryu"
msgid "And you can finally stop trying to scream over him. But\\r\nyeah, he's calm now."
msgstr "Y al fin puedes dejar de intentar gritar más que él. Pero\\r\nsí, ya se calmó."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "92_Date"
msgid "Man... I feel like just a few hours of that shaved years off my life."
msgstr "Amigo... me siento como si unas horas de esto me hubieran \\r\nsacado años de vida."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "104_Kiryu"
msgid "Nothing a few drinks can't fix. Anyway, where'd this kid come from?"
msgstr "Nada que unas copas no puedan arreglar. Bueno, ¿de dónde \\r\nsalió este pequeño?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "116_Date"
msgid "Oh yeah, I never told you, did I?"
msgstr "Ah sí, no te llegué a contar, ¿no?"

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "128_Date"
msgid "Well, when I came over to the bar earlier, I heard this\\r\nnoise coming from the back alley."
msgstr "Bueno, cuando llegué antes al bar, escuché \\r\nun ruido que provenía del callejón de atrás."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "140_Date"
msgid "And when I went to take a look, I found this baby lying on\\r\nthe back steps. Almost like somebody hid him there. It was bizarre."
msgstr "Y cuando fuí a echar un vistazo, me encontré este bebé \\r\nestirado sobre la escalera trasera. Como si alguien lo \\r\nhubiese dejado ahí. Muy extraño."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "152_Date"
msgid "He was crying like a damn banshee, too. I didn't know what\\r\nto do... so I brought him in."
msgstr "Lloraba como un alma en pena. No sabía qué hacer...\\r\nasí que lo traje dentro."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "164_Kiryu"
msgid "You said it looked like he was hidden there? That doesn't\\r\nsound like your run-of-the-mill abandoned baby. Did they leave a note?"
msgstr "¿Decías que parecía como si estuviera escondido? No parece\\r\nel típico caso de bebé abandonado. ¿Dejaron una nota?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "176_Date"
msgid "You know, I didn't even think to check. Lemme go take a look."
msgstr "Sabes, no pensé ni en comprobarlo. Déjame ir a ver."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:translated_by=sasha
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "200_Date"
msgid "Here we go. Found something. This handwriting's awful,\\r\nthough. Whoever wrote it was sure in a hurry."
msgstr "Aquí está. Encontré algo. Muy mala caligrafía.\\r\nQuien sea que lo haya escrito estaba en un buen apuro."

#. y4:line_status=reviewed
#. y4:reviewed_by=sasha
msgctxt "212_Kiryu"
msgid "What does it say?"
msgstr "¿Qué dice?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "224_Date"
msgid "\"Please take care of my baby. And, I'm sorry.\""
msgstr "\"Por favor, cuide a mi bebé. Y lo siento.\""

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "236_Kiryu"
msgid "We should bring him to the police."
msgstr "Deberíamos llevarlo a la policía."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "248_Date"
msgid "I mean, yeah... but then we'll be stuck at the station 'til\\r\nthey make sure everything checks out."
msgstr "A ver, sí... pero no nos dejaran salir de comisaría hasta\\r\nque se aseguren que todo está en orden."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "260_Date"
msgid "You ask me, whoever left him here has got to be still in\\r\ntown. Let's go out and look for them."
msgstr "Si me preguntas a mí, quien sea que lo haya dejado aquí \\r\ndebe seguir en la ciudad. Vamos a buscarle."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "272_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah, not a bad idea."
msgstr "Sí, no es mala idea."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "284_Date"
msgid "But I will say, with how many people we've got here... I'd\\r\nhave thought <Italic>somebody</Italic> would have been able to get him to\\r\nstop crying."
msgstr "Eso sí, con todos los que somos... Hubiera creído que \\r\n<Italic>alguien</Italic> fuera capaz de que dejara\\r\nde llorar."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "296_Akiyama"
msgid "Sorry, kids aren't really my forte."
msgstr "Lo siento, los niños no son mi punto fuerte."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "320_Saejima"
msgid "...He'd just cry more if he saw my mug starin' back at him."
msgstr "...Hubiera llorado más si me llega a ver el careto de frente."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "344_Tanimura"
msgid "I think you're just the nurturing father this kid was looking for, Date-san."
msgstr "Yo creo que eras el padre idílico que necesitaba, Date."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "368_Date"
msgid "*sigh* Forget it. We just need to focus on finding whoever\\r\ndropped this kid off. There must be someone nearby who saw\\r\nthem do it."
msgstr "*suspira* En fin. Tenemos que concentrarnos en encontrar\\r\na quien haya dejado al niño tirado. Tiene que haber alguien\\r\ncerca que lo haya visto."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "380_Tanimura"
msgid "I'll handle it. I'm a detective, after all. If this doesn't\\r\nfall under the jurisdiction of Community Safety, I don't\\r\nknow what would."
msgstr "Yo me ocupo. Al fin y al cabo, soy detective. Si esto no\\r\ncae dentro de mi jurisdicción de Seguridad de la \\r\nComunidad, no sé qué otra cosa me queda."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "392_Date"
msgid "Forget it. You're supposed to be \"dead,\" remember?"
msgstr "Ni lo sueñes. Se supone que estás 'muerto', ¿recuerdas?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "404_Tanimura"
msgid "Oops."
msgstr "Ups."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "416_Date"
msgid "Oops is right. The police would get wind of you flashing\\r\nyour badge around in a heartbeat."
msgstr "Exacto, 'ups'. La policía no tardaría en oír sobre ti\\r\nenseñando la placa por ahí como si nada."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "428_Tanimura"
msgid "I guess you're right. But we don't really have anyone else\\r\nwho's capable enough."
msgstr "Supongo que tienes razón. Pero realmente no tenemos a\\r\nnadie más que tenga la capacidad de hacerlo."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "440_Date"
msgid "What, the escaped convict and troubled moneylender don't strike confidence into your heart?"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿Acaso el convicto fugado y el prestamista en \\r\nproblemas no te generan confianza?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "452_Akiyama"
msgid "You hear what he's saying about us?"
msgstr "¿Has oído lo que nos ha llamado?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "464_Saejima"
msgid "Sure as hell do."
msgstr "Te aseguro que sí."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "476_Date"
msgid "Guess I'll just have to head out there myself."
msgstr "Supongo que me toca a mí."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "488_Kiryu"
msgid "No, I'll do it."
msgstr "No, yo lo haré."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "500_Date"
msgid "Huh? Why?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Por qué?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "512_Kiryu"
msgid "I've had enough piss on my face tonight to last a lifetime.\\r\nHe's all yours, Date."
msgstr "Ya tengo el suficiente pis en la cara para el resto de mi \\r\nvida. Es todo tuyo, Date."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "524_Date"
msgid "Hey, you can't just dump him on me like this!"
msgstr "¡Oye, no puedes dejármelo a mi así como así!"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "536_Kiryu"
msgid "Let's just say we're even now. Good luck."
msgstr "Digamos que ahora estamos en paz. Buena suerte."

